3 VARIANT
1. Advanced Optimization:
CartItemListAPIView da select_related va prefetch_relateddan foydalanib, product,
seller va mahsulotning barcha rasmlarini jami 2-3 ta queryda yuklang.

2. Password Safety:
UserChangePasswordModelSerializerda yangi parol eski parol bilan bir xil bo‘lib qolmasligini tekshiruvchi validator yozing.

3. Ownership Permission:
Sotuvchi faqat o‘ziga tegishli mahsulotlarni tahrirlashi (patch) yoki o‘chirishi uchun IsProductOwner permission-ni yarating va Product ViewSet-ga qo‘shing.

4. Dynamic Fields:
ProductListModelSerializerdan foydalanib, foydalanuvchi so‘rovda yuborgan fieldlarini
(masalan: ?fields=id,name) dinamik ravishda qaytaruvchi mantiqni View’da qo‘llang.

5. Price Range Filter: ProductFilterSetda mahsulotlarni min_price va max_price (narx oralig‘i) bo‘yicha filtrlashni django-filter orqali amalga oshiring.


